event Add(uint256 indexed fid, uint32 indexed keyType, bytes indexed key, bytes keyBytes, uint8 metadataType, bytes metadata)
event Remove(uint256 indexed fid, bytes indexed key, bytes keyBytes)
event AdminReset(uint256 indexed fid, bytes indexed key, bytes keyBytes)
event SetValidator(uint32 keyType, uint8 metadataType, address oldValidator, address newValidator)
function totalKeys(uint256 fid, uint8 state) external view returns (uint256)
function keyAt(uint256 fid, uint8 state, uint256 index) external view returns (bytes)
function keysOf(uint256 fid, uint8 state) external view returns (bytes[])
function keyDataOf(uint256 fid, bytes calldata key) external view returns (address)
function removeFor(address fidOwner, bytes calldata key, uint256 deadline, bytes calldata sig) external
